data.description: ''Easy on the Eyes''' This 3 Bdrm, w/ Den, 2 bath, Great room, Split Flrplan Is Loaded w/ Recent Renovations & Is Located 3.3 Acres In the Popular,Scenic Community of Hidden Valley.The Property is Encased w/ Serine Moutain Views, Stunning Sunsets, & Lots of Riding & Hiking Trails. The Recently Constructed Metal Shade/Shed Row Offers The Perfect Place For Horses & Other Livestock. The Lg Water Storage Tank w/ New Pump Makes Water Storage & Distribution Easy! The Newer Roof & Newer AC Add To The Excellence Of This Inviting Home. The Multi Purpose, Handicap Accessible Deck Allows A Tranquil Place To Enjoy Amazing Sunsets.The Interior Shines Like Chrome:Newer Flooring, Paint, Carpet, Plumbing, Upgraded Cabinetry Through Out & The Quartz Countertops In The Kitchen Are Awesome Finishing Touches
